(42, 5, 17, 40, 11, 5, 5, 'the power of the Lord was present to heal them', 'Healing and Gospel Preaching', 'This connection highlights the theme of healing and restoration present in both passages. Luke 5:17 mentions the power of the Lord to heal, while Matthew 11:5 lists various healings and the preaching of the gospel.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 5, 17, 44, 19, 11, 11, 'the power of the Lord was present', 'Miraculous Healing Power', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine power manifesting through human agents. In both passages, the presence of God''s power is emphasized, with Luke noting the healing power during Jesus'' teaching and Acts describing miracles performed by Paul.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
